<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Anagram · Scrabble Words Finder · English Solver</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Every competitive Scrabble player has a rating — a number that reflects their playing strength. Like chess Elo, Scrabble ratings rise when you win and drop when you lose. Understanding how the system works helps you set realistic goals, choose appropriate tournaments, and track your improvement over time.</p>

